\int_0^{\pi/2} \sin^{2n} x dx = - \frac{\sin^{2n-1} x \cos x}{2n}|_0^{\pi/2}+\frac{2n-1}{2n}\int_0^{\pi/2} \sin^{2n-2} xdx
